HEADWORD: Significate
<hw>Sig*nif"i*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>significatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>significare</ets>. See
<er>Signify</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Logic)</fld> <def>One of several things
